# =============================================================================
# .clinerules - Arabic AP Invoice Processing Specification
# Arabic Language Accounts Payable Automation
# =============================================================================
# This specification defines the HITL (Human-in-the-Loop) system for processing
# Arabic language accounts payable invoices with AI-assisted extraction.
# =============================================================================

# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# SPECIFICATION OVERVIEW
# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------

## Purpose

The Arabic AP Invoice Processing specification defines:
- **OCR Processing**: Arabic script recognition and extraction
- **Field Extraction**: Invoice data field identification
- **HITL Workflow**: Human review and correction process
- **Quality Assurance**: Extraction accuracy validation

## Key Documents

| Document | Purpose |
|----------|---------|
| `arabic-ap-spec.tex` | Main specification document |
| `chapters/03-extraction-pipeline.tex` | OCR and extraction flow |
| `chapters/05-hitl-workflow.tex` | Human review workflow |
| `chapters/07-quality-metrics.tex` | Quality measurement |

